 yr. For the LMC, this lifetime is $\\sim 3 \\times 10^5$\nyr. The superwind phase traced with Spitzer lasts for $\\sim 10^4$ yr. Spitzer\nspectra of a K supergiant and a compact HII region are also given.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 2 Nov 2006 19:58:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2008-11-26"}
