lity and several environmental\nmechanisms, fuelled by organic inputs and leading to seagrass loss. Coupling\ndirect measurements of benthic sedimentation rates with dynamics of key species\nis proposed as an efficient way to predict and minimize fish farm impacts to\nbenthic communities.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 2 Nov 2006 16:21:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2007-05-23"}
